OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F359A1776596567
OL,3,CVolunteers mount horses to tackle fly
OL,4,Ccamping and anti-social behaviour in
OL,5,CLakes
OL,7,FVolunteers are saddling up to aid
OL,8,Fpolice officers in tackling illegal
OL,9,Fcamping in and around the Lake
OL,10,FDistrict.
OL,12,FCumbria Police is using 10 mounted
OL,13,Fsupport volunteers to spread
OL,14,FCountryside Code messages to visitors,
OL,15,Fand act as community "eyes and ears".
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G1/7
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,360,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F359A1776596567
OL,3,CVolunteers mount horses to tackle fly
OL,4,Ccamping and anti-social behaviour in
OL,5,CLakes
OL,7,FThis initiative comes after local
OL,8,Fresidents have repeatedly highlighted
OL,9,Flittering, abandoned equipment, and
OL,10,Fanti-social behaviour, which led to
OL,11,FWestmorland and Furness Council
OL,12,Fexpanding its powers to issue fines.
OL,14,FOne volunteer, Amanda Wallace, says
OL,15,Fthe use of horses can help "break down
OL,16,Fbarriers" when explaining what is and
OL,17,Fis not allowed in the countryside.
OL,19,FVolunteers own their horses, and
OL,20,FAmanda's steed is 10-year-old Murphy.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/7
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,360,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F359A1776596567
OL,3,CVolunteers mount horses to tackle fly
OL,4,Ccamping and anti-social behaviour in
OL,5,CLakes
OL,7,FMs Wallace said: "Having Murphy there
OL,8,Fis a real ice-breaker. He will stand
OL,9,Fand let kids stroke him and pat him,
OL,10,Fand then you can have those open
OL,11,Fconversations with people.
OL,13,F"If we can use our volunteer sector to
OL,14,Fhelp educate and chat, and break down
OL,15,Fthose barriers, it's really helpful
OL,16,Fand that's the plan this summer.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/7
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,360,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F359A1776596567
OL,3,CVolunteers mount horses to tackle fly
OL,4,Ccamping and anti-social behaviour in
OL,5,CLakes
OL,7,F"There are significant problems with
OL,8,Fpeople leaving litter behind or
OL,9,Fstarting fires and chopping trees
OL,10,Fdown. We also see social media posts
OL,11,Fabout tents et cetera being left
OL,12,Fbehind.
OL,14,F"People who visit should leave no
OL,15,Ftrace and this is another tool to help
OL,16,Fget that message out there."
OL,18,FVolunteers can report criminal
OL,19,Fincidents to police, and alert
OL,20,Fcouncils to incidents such as fly-
OL,21,Ftipping or abandoned vehicles.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G4/7
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,360,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F359A1776596567
OL,3,CVolunteers mount horses to tackle fly
OL,4,Ccamping and anti-social behaviour in
OL,5,CLakes
OL,7,FMs Wallace has worked as a mounted
OL,8,Fsupport volunteer for two years, and
OL,9,Fshe has an equestrian background.
OL,11,FShe said the role is "an opportunity
OL,12,Fto be part of the community", and
OL,13,Fclarify to visitors "what is or isn't
OL,14,Fallowed".
OL,16,FMs Wallace said: "Hopefully we can
OL,17,Fpush the message out. We're never
OL,18,Fgoing to stop it (completely), but I
OL,19,Fthink we can make things better.
OL,26,@zD@RpmzD@]pn
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G5/7
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,360,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F359A1776596567
OL,3,CVolunteers mount horses to tackle fly
OL,4,Ccamping and anti-social behaviour in
OL,5,CLakes
OL,7,F"Although (as volunteers) we don't
OL,8,Fhave any enforcement powers, we can
OL,9,Ffurnish people with the information
OL,10,Fand advise them about what's right and
OL,11,Fwrong, and what could happen if they
OL,12,Fdo X, Y or Z.
OL,14,F"We're the eyes and ears of the
OL,15,Fcommunity."
OL,26,@oD@KpmoD@Ypn
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G6/7
